parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or refuse to shift gears, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or refuses to shift gears
the overdrive light flashes
the transmission slips or jerks
the vehicle loses power or acceleration
and the gear shift lever breaks off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the gear shift lever can cause the vehicle to become stuck in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The gear shift lever breaks off
the vehicle becomes stuck in gear
and the driver is unable to shift into park or other gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle's systems to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The overdrive light flashes
the check engine light stays on
and the seat belt light stays on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the body and corrosion issues can cause structural components to fail, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Rust and corrosion on the rear of the truck
failure or detachment of exterior body components
and structural components may present a safety hazard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear lift gate can cause the gate to fall off, shatter, or crack, leading to potential injuries or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: Cracks in the rear lift gate panel
shattered rear window
door ajar warning light
and failure of the lift gate to latch securely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The shattering of the rear window can cause injuries or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: Shattered rear window
door ajar warning light
and failure of the lift gate to latch securely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hood support struts can cause severe head, hand, or arm injuries.
symptoms: Hood falling down without warning or notice.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The peeling of the dashboard can cause cosmetic issues and potentially lead to other problems.
symptoms: Peeling of the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear coil springs can cause the vehicle to become unstable, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle's stance changes
the rear springs are cracked or broken
and the vehicle may vibrate or make a loud noise while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wheel bearings can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, and can also cause damage to other components, such as the transmission and suspension.
symptoms: Loud roaring or grinding noise from the wheels
vibration while driving
and difficulty steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power and stall, leading to accidents, and can also cause damage to other components.
symptoms: Slipping or hesitation when shifting gears
vibration while driving
and difficulty accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents, and can also cause damage to other components.
symptoms: Spongy brake pedal
difficulty stopping
and grinding noise when applying the brakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various components to malfunction, leading to accidents, and can also cause damage to other components.
symptoms: Faulty horn
power locks
radio
and interior lights not functioning properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the suspension can cause the vehicle to become unstable, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: Clunking noise from the suspension
vibration while driving
and difficulty steering.
